reviewText: Love this series. Watched season 1 and most of season two on Mhz choice before they took it off. It's real, it's clean, it's  honest.

This is a great series.  I rented the first series from Netflix but they did not have the second or third available so I just had to buy them.  I love how "real" the characters are along with how funny and moving the storylines and situations are.  You really feel like you are getting to know them.
